The paper deals with spectrum optimization in multi-user multi-carrier communication systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a novel class of iterative approximation methods, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper deals with multi-user systems, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM).
